values:
I feel like no matter what is going on, it gets harder and harder to catch up and keep up to date here on Livejournal. I wish I had more time but I just don't. I miss you all so much and it makes me so sad to say I think my days of updating regularly on here are long gone. I'm not deleting my journal and I will still be reading as often as I can, and trying to comment and I will probably update here and there but in the mean time, I wanted to let you all know how to reach me on other social media sites that I am much more active on. Twitter: ifyouseekelsey Instagram: ifyouseekelsey Tumblr: ifyouseekelsey ANDDDD... Kelsey Brandenburg

Create Your Badge Please add me on any and all of these if you haven't already. I love you all so much. Please don't remove me (unless my lack of updates will bother you for whatever reason) because I do really love reading about all of your lives. ♥

I want everyone who comes across this post to leave an anonymous comment saying anything you want.
A secret, a story, an opinion, anything. You can be brutally honest.
Not that I'm not interested in what you have to say, but I'm also really curious as to how many people read or come across this journal.

"Why can't we get all the people together in the world that we really like and then just stay together? I guess that wouldn't work. Someone would leave. Someone always leaves and then we have to say good-bye. I hate good-byes. I know what I need. I need more hellos."


FRIENDS ONLY. ♥
Comment & ask to be added/tell me how you found my LJ.
Add me first or else I probably won't notice you've added me. I love new people.
